-loc=\"89:38\"> <h2 data-astro-cid-xfsepetq data-astro-source-file=\"C:/Users/FingerWeg/CascadeProjects/podcast/src/layouts/EpisodeLayout.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"90:15\">Share</h2> <div class=\"share-actions\" data-astro-cid-xfsepetq data-astro-source-file=\"C:/Users/FingerWeg/CascadeProjects/podcast/src/layouts/EpisodeLayout.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"91:38\"> <button type=\"button\" data-share-link data-astro-cid-xfsepetq data-astro-source-file=\"C:/Users/FingerWeg/CascadeProjects/podcast/src/layouts/EpisodeLayout.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"92:51\">Share episode</button> <button type=\"button\" data-copy-link data-astro-cid-xfsepetq data-astro-source-file=\"C:/Users/FingerWeg/CascadeProjects/podcast/src/layouts/EpisodeLayout.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"93:50\">Copy link</button> </div> </section>  </aside> </section> <nav class=\"episode-nav reveal\" aria-label=\"Episode navigation\" data-astro-cid-xfsepetq data-astro-source-file=\"C:/Users/FingerWeg/CascadeProjects/podcast/src/layouts/EpisodeLayout.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"107:71\"> <span data-astro-cid-xfsepetq data-astro-source-file=\"C:/Users/FingerWeg/CascadeProjects/podcast/src/layouts/EpisodeLayout.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"114:12\"></span> <a class=\"card\" href=\"/shows/the-deep-end/antikythera-mechanism/\" data-astro-cid-xfsepetq data-astro-source-file=\"C:/Users/FingerWeg/CascadeProjects/podcast/src/layouts/EpisodeLayout.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"117:81\"> <span data-astro-cid-xfsepetq data-astro-source-file=\"C:/Users/FingerWeg/CascadeProjects/podcast/src/layouts/EpisodeLayout.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"118:19\">Older</span> <strong data-astro-cid-xfsepetq data-astro-source-file=\"C:/Users/FingerWeg/CascadeProjects/podcast/src/layouts/EpisodeLayout.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"119:21\">The Antikythera Mechanism: Diving for Ancient Computers</strong> </a> </nav> </article> <script>\n    const pathname = window.location.pathname;\n    const canonical = `${window.location.origin}${pathname}`;\n\n    document.querySelector('[data-copy-link]')?.addEventListener('click', async () => {\n      await navigator.clipboard.writeText(canonical);\n    });\n\n    document.querySelector('[data-share-link]')?.addEventListener('click', async () => {\n      if (navigator.share) {\n        await navigator.share({\n          title: document.title,\n          url: canonical,\n        });\n        return;\n      }\n      await navigator.clipboard.writeText(canonical);\n    });\n\n    const transcriptPanel = document.querySelector('[data-transcript-panel]');\n    if (transcriptPanel) {\n      transcriptPanel.addEventListener('toggle', async (event) => {\n        const panel = event.currentTarget;\n        if (!panel.open || panel.dataset.loaded === 'true') {\n          return;\n        }\n        const output = panel.querySelector('[data-transcript-output]');\n        output.textContent = 'Loading transcript...';\n\n        try {\n          const response = await fetch(panel.dataset.transcriptUrl);\n          output.textContent = await response.text();\n          panel.dataset.loaded = 'true';\n        } catch (error) {\n          output.textContent = `Transcript failed to load: ${error.message}`;\n        }\n      });\n    }\n  </script>  </main> <footer class=\"site-footer\" data-astro-cid-sz7xmlte data-astro-source-file=\"C:/Users/FingerWeg/CascadeProjects/podcast/src/components/Footer.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"16:29\"> <div class=\"shell footer-grid\" data-astro-cid-sz7xmlte data-astro-source-file=\"C:/Users/FingerWeg/CascadeProjects/podcast/src/components/Footer.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"17:34\"> <section data-astro-cid-sz7xmlte data-astro-source-file=\"C:/Users/FingerWeg/CascadeProjects/podcast/src/components/Footer.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"18:14\"> <h2 data-astro-cid-sz7xmlte data-astro-source-file=\"C:/Users/FingerWeg/CascadeProjects/podcast/src/components/Footer.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"19:11\">Archive S